691
00:42:52,528 --> 00:42:55,114
You took credit for someone else's

692
00:42:55,739 --> 00:42:57,116
intuitive decision

693
00:42:57,658 --> 00:42:58,909
and excellent reasoning.

694
00:42:59,618 --> 00:43:00,828
That's plagiarism.

695
00:43:01,412 --> 00:43:02,454
