696
00:43:04,164 --> 00:43:05,374
Show-off.

697
00:43:05,874 --> 00:43:08,377
Whatever. Let's go have some tteokgalbi.

698
00:43:08,877 --> 00:43:11,297
-I found a great restaurant.
-I don't like tteokgalbi.

