700
00:43:14,466 --> 00:43:15,718
Haenam.

701
00:43:15,801 --> 00:43:16,677
Haenam…

702
00:43:18,929 --> 00:43:20,306
Can I record a mukbang there?

703
00:43:21,515 --> 00:43:22,933
Okay.

704
00:43:23,517 --> 00:43:25,394
